<Paragraph>
Essential XlsIO now supports the insertion of OLE objects. This sample demonstrates how an OLE object can be inserted. It is possible to embed the object, or insert it as a link. For both types, location and size can be adjusted.
</Paragraph>

<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">Features:</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Ability to Insert OLE objects.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Ability to adjust position.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Ability to adjust size.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

